  "title": "Glowing Ores Animated",
  "description": "Best Animated glowing ores texture pack so that people can notice ores quickly. This makes ores outlined, animated + glowing",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1377815/description_9bf91f3f-1aa2-4670-a1f5-44a2c88c394d.png\" alt=\"header decoration\"></p>\n<p>Bring your mining adventures to life with Animated Glowing Ores! Every ore is outlined, illuminated, and smoothly animated &mdash; turning the dull stone walls of your cave into a vibrant treasure map.This pack makes all ores easy to spot, even in pitch-black caves. Each ore type has its own unique glowing color and a subtle pulse animation, so you&rsquo;ll instantly recognize diamonds, redstone, and emeralds from afar.</p>\n<p>💎 Features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Full animation + glowing outlines for every ore (Overworld + Deepslate).</li>\n<li>Works perfectly with OptiFine or emissive texture support.</li>\n<li>Optimized for visibility &ndash; find ores quickly without breaking immersion.</li>\n<li>Compatible with most shaders and other texture packs.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 55, 42);\"><strong>Optifine Needed</strong></span></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_121f26fd-71f6-44f9-a9fa-3921bb07e0f9.png\"  alt=\"beautifull Glowing Ores\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_28a44775-3412-409a-8951-e2e2695cec06.png\"  alt=\"beautifull Glowing Ores\"></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Socials:</span></strong></h1>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Join our discord&nbsp;</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://discord.gg/mYfhfWtH8v\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><u><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1238974/description_ab71df94-6fc9-41c3-ae8b-b021beb72514.png\" alt=\"end\"></u></a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@NetherSparkStudios\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">✅ Allowed with My Projects</a></strong></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li><strong>You can showcase my work in videos/streams if you give proper credit (e.g., link to the official download).</strong></li>\n<li><strong>You can edit file for personal use only</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>❌ Not Allowed with My Projects</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>You cannot distribute through monetized links (AdFly, Linkvertise, etc.).</strong></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>You cannot edit and re-share my projects&nbsp;</strong></li>\n</ul>",
